# Severance knowledge (agent reference)

Read [`.cursor/knowledge/severance-facts.md`](../knowledge/severance-facts.md) and [`.cursor/knowledge/show-app-continuity.md`](../knowledge/show-app-continuity.md) before changing copy, ambient events, MDR visuals, or Lumon branding.

**Voice rules**
- Clinical corporate handbook tone; short imperative lines
- Prefer: refinement, compliance, department, Board, workstation, file, quota, temper
- Avoid: generic “habit tracker,” “pet,” gamey “level up,” purple cyber neon
- Easter eggs = lore crumbs; CR/XP rewards stay tiny

**Visual rules**
- MDR = scary numbers, temper quadrants (WO/FC/DR/MA), phosphor CRT
- Office = sage carpet, white panels, ceiling grid, 4-pod desks
- Ambient stays rare (hours-scale), not arcade
